@model kerrwed.Models.RsvpModel
@{
  ViewBag.Title = "Kerr Wedding in Puerto Morelos, Mexico use Sun Country Promo Code";
}

<section class="tuckUnder">
  <img style="position:absolute; top:5%; right:5%; width: 40%;z-index: 1000" src="~/Content/images/heart.png" />
  <img class="fullWidthImage" src="~/Content/images/hotel-marina-el-cid-pier.jpg" />
</section>

<section class="content">
  <div class="soExcited">
    <p>We are so excited to share our special day with our family and friends!</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Location</h2>
  <p>Our destination wedding will take place on February 14, 2015 at <a href="http://www.elcid.com/marina_beach_resort/" target="_blank" title="Hotel Marina El Cid Spa & Beach Resort">Hotel Marina El Cid Spa & Beach Resort</a> in Puerto Morelos, Mexico.  Puerto Morelos is 27km (17 miles) south of Cancun's international airport (CUN).
  This is a family friendly all-inclusive resort that features a kids club.  The resort also has an adult only pool.  Children are welcome, Hudson and Hailey will be attending.</p>
  <p>
    We are travelling from February 12th through February 19th. The ceremony will take place at the beach with a reception following immediately after.  The wedding attire is beach chic.
  </p>
  <p>Please <a href="#rsvp" title="RSVP">RSVP</a> by January 16th, 2015</p>
</section>

<div class="wavesDivider"></div>

<section class="content">
  <h2>Travel Information</h2>
  <h3>Sun Country Vacations</h3>
  <p>The Hotel Marina El Cid Spa & Resort is a vacation package destination for Sun Country airlines. We have a group discount rate available if you book through Sun Country Vacations using promo code <span class="promoCode">TPSLYV0928</span>.</p>
  <ul>
    <li> $25 discount on air and hotel packages of $699–$999</li>
    <li> $50 discount on air and hotel packages of $1,000–$2,499 </li>
    <li>$100 discount on air and hotel packages of $2,500–$4,999</li>
    <li>$200 discount on air and hotel packages of $5,000 or more</li>
  </ul>
  <h3>How to Use the Sun County Vacations Promo Code</h3>
  <p>
    To use the Sun Country promo code you must stay at Hotel Marina El Cid Spa & Resort and you must travel between 2/09/2015 and 2/22/2015.  For questions or to book your vacation visit <a href="http://suncountryvacations.com" target="_blank" title="Sun Country Vacations Promo Code TPSLYV0928">suncountryvacations.com</a> or call 1-877-411-1177 prompt 1 then 2 or contact your travel agent.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you choose to book online, run a search for Sun Country Vacation packages for travel to Cancun, Mexico.  Select the The Hotel Marina El Cid Spa & Resort as your resort and choose your desired flights and room type.  There is an option to apply a promo code near the end of the checkout before you enter payment information.  Enter promo code <span class="promoCode">TPSLYV0928</span> and click "Apply."
  </p>
</section>

<div class="wavesDivider"></div>

<section class="content">
  <h2>About the Couple</h2>
  <h3>Sara</h3>
  <p>Sara is a Registered Nurse in the Post Anesthesia Care Unit at University of Minnesota Medical Center, Fairview in Minneapolis, MN.  She enjoys running and being active.  Sara also has a beautiful Siamese cat whom she loves very much.  </p>
  <h3>Jonathan</h3>
  <p>Jonathan grew up in Canada and moved to Minnesota to play hockey at Minnesota State University, Mankato.   Not only is he a great hockey player, but also a loving father to Hudson (9) and Hailey (8).  Jonathan is a Senior Developer at Marketing Architects in Minnetonka, MN.</p>
  <h3>How We Met</h3>
  <p>Sara and Jonathan met through a mutual friend.  As neighbors on Lake Calhoun, they ended up spending a lot of time together.</p>

  <h3>How We Got Engaged</h3>
  <p>Jonathan and Sara traveled to Cancun, Mexico over New Year's in 2013 to escape the winter.  Shortly after midnight, Jonathan brought Sara to the lifeguard tower by the beach and popped the question.  </p>

  <h3 style="margin-top: 30px">Gift Registry</h3>
  <p>Your presence is the only gift desired.</p>
  <h3 style="margin-top: 30px">Helpful Links</h3>
  <ul class="noBullets">
    <li>
      <a href="http://www.elcid.com/marina_beach_resort/" target="_blank" title="Hotel Marina El Cid Spa & Beach Resort">Hotel Marina El Cid Spa & Beach Resort</a>
    </li>
    <li><a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Hotel+Marina+El+Cid+Spa+%26+Beach+Resort/&#64;20.834871,-86.889793,10z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x8f4e883a1acc0021:0x1cbf32f17a64beb4" title="Hotel Marina El Cid Resort and Spa on Google Maps" target="_blank">Resort Location on Google Maps</a></li>
    <li>
      <a href="http://www.suncountry.com/page/1/sun-country-vacations.jsp/" target="_blank" title="Sun Country Vacations">Sun Country Vacations</a>
